177
00:16:04,679 --> 00:16:06,559
Menusuk hati
semua petarung Suchuan.

178
00:16:07,879 --> 00:16:09,879
Darah segar mengalir bagai
bendung yang pecah.

179
00:16:10,559 --> 00:16:12,320
